# claude/

Plugin that integrates Claude Code skills and subagents with Intent project management. Provides commands for managing subagents, skills, project rules, code reviews via critics, and project LLM guidance through upgrade workflows.

## Files

- `plugin.json` -- Plugin manifest with command registry (subagents, skills, rules, audit, modules, upgrade, prime)
- `bin/intent_claude` -- Command dispatcher for claude subcommands (subagents, skills, upgrade, rules, prime)
- `bin/intent_audit` -- Quick automated code quality checks (dispatches to critic-* agents)
- `bin/intent_modules` -- Module registry guardrails (check, find; enforces the Highlander Rule)
- `lib/claude_subagents.sh` -- Subagent lifecycle (init, list, install, sync, uninstall, show, status)
- `lib/claude_skills.sh` -- Skills lifecycle (list, install, sync, uninstall, show)
- `lib/claude_rules.sh` -- Rules enumeration, show, validate, and indexing (canon + extensions)
- `lib/claude_upgrade.sh` -- Diagnose and apply LLM guidance upgrades to project files
- `lib/claude_prime.sh` -- Pre-load project memory with rules, modules, and operational knowledge
- `rules/` -- Intent rules library organized by language (elixir/, rust/, swift/, lua/, shell/; schema/)
